story: Pwnky, a creature from the Black night of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Red eyes eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Sad mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Golden ears ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Hidden hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Hat with leafs  hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Horns, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Black night, Red eyes, Mechanic body, Sad, Golden ears, Hidden hair, Hat with leafs , Horns
